          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 148,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Divers can often make large amounts of money by diving for treasures and selling them at a markup to tourists and antiquities dealers.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
